<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Secondary on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/secondary/</link><description>Recent content in Secondary on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/secondary/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MongoDB - not primary - read preference error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/mongodb-replica-set-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/mongodb-replica-set-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A &amp;ldquo;not primary&amp;rdquo; read preference error occurs when a read operation is sent to a secondary replica set member that is not configured to accept reads, or when the primary node is unavailable and read preference is not set for secondaries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Default read preference sends reads to primary only&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Primary node is down and no secondary accepts reads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secondary node not configured with &lt;code&gt;readPreference: secondary&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operations that require primary (e.g., writes) sent to secondary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;readConcern&lt;/code&gt; level incompatible with read preference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set read preference for secondary reads:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;analytics&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;readPreference&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ReadPreference&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;SECONDARY_PREFERRED&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;results&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;find&lt;/span&gt;({}).&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toArray&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use read preference tags for data center routing:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;secondaryInDC&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ReadPreference&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;secondary&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, [
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;region&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;us-east&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;dc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;secondary&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;]);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;logs&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;readPreference&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;secondaryInDC&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle primary not available:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;userId&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;code&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10107&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;includes&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;not primary&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fallback to secondary read
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;readPreference&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ReadPreference&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;SECONDARY_PREFERRED&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;userId&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure read concern with secondaries:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;events&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;find&lt;/span&gt;({})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;readConcern&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;majority&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toArray&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check replica set status:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;admin&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;replSetGetStatus&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Primary:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;members&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;find&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;stateStr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;PRIMARY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Error: not primary and secondaryOk=false
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// When connected to secondary without read preference
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: set read preference
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;readPreference&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ReadPreference&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;SECONDARY_PREFERRED&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/mongodb-replica-set-error-v2/"&gt;Replica set error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/mongodb-connection-error/"&gt;Connection error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>MongoDB OplogWindowTooSmall: oplog window exhausted</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/oplog-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/oplog-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when a secondary member in a replica set cannot keep up with the primary and falls out of the oplog window. The secondary must do a full initial sync to rejoin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write volume exceeds the secondary&amp;rsquo;s replication throughput&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oplog size is too small for the amount of write activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secondary hardware is underpowered (CPU, disk I/O)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network latency between primary and secondary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check current oplog window size:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printReplicationInfo&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// primary
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printSecondaryReplicationInfo&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// secondaries
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resize the oplog on the primary:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;runCommand&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;replSetResizeOplog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 16 GB
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor replication lag:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
